 2000-13992000-09-060INDUSTRY,  ,  ,  , 
PrecisAppointment of GEORGE WILLISTON MacDONALD, of Halifax, Nova Scotia, JOHN MacDONALD, of Manotick, Ontario, and MARGO BUCHANAN, of Antigonish, Nova Scotia, as directors of the Board of Directors of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, to hold office during pleasure, for a term of three years, or until the dissolution of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, whichever occurs first.
